SavouryPot is a wonderful recipe manager. Keep all your recipes in SavouryPot, creating a personal cookbook. 

• Save and organize your own recipes;
• Import recipes from websites;
• Scan recipes from your favourite books and magazines;
• Feel the benefits of iCloud synchronization;
• Take photos of your dishes and enjoy the magnificent view of recipes; 
• Find necessary recipes quickly with a smart search;
• Scale recipes to cook a particular amount;
• Cook comfortably using a special cook mode;
• Set up timers in one tap;
• Use one recipe as an ingredient of another;
• Add ingredients into SavouryList - our free shopping list application;

You can write a recipe manually or import recipes from websites with an intelligent universal algorithm, which works seemlessly with most websites.
